      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARRY ON MACI (6) goes very well this trip starting 12 times for seven wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (22.68) when second at Warragul in a Free For All. Expected to go close. PAW SAKAKIBURA (8) should enjoy clear running from the outside box. Below best latest at this track (19.65) when 7th and beaten 4.5 lengths. Form here at this distance is strong including three wins. Has ability and can measure up. WINKING WILLIE (7) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, winding up to place two back then finishing on strongly last time when second (23.04) in a Special conditions Veteran race at Warragul. Has a good record at this journey. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Hard to beat again. PRINCE LAROI (3) scored by a neck last time (16.77) in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track. Has already won out of this draw.",
